TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed AutoCompleteType extends System.Enum

summary.span: 表示控制 控件中自动完成功能的行为的值。

span.span: Represents the values that control the behavior of the AutoComplete feature in a control.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 为了帮助输入数据，Internet Explorer 5 和更高版本以及其他一些浏览器支持名为自动完成的功能。To assist with data entry, Internet Explorer 5 and later and some other browsers support a feature named AutoComplete. "自动完成" 监视文本框，并存储用户输入的值的列表。AutoComplete monitors a text box and stores a list of the values that the user has entered. 当用户另一次返回文本框时，将显示值列表。When the user returns to the text box another time, the list of values is displayed. 用户只需从此列表中选择值，而无需重新键入值。Instead of retyping a value, the user can simply select the value from this list. > [!NOTE] > 并非所有浏览器都支持自动完成功能。Not all browsers support the AutoComplete feature. 查看浏览器以确定兼容性。Check with your browser to determine compatibility. 若要控制控件的自动完成功能的行为 ，请使用 属性。To control the behavior of the AutoComplete feature for a control, you use the property. 枚举用于表示可应用于属性的值 。The enumeration is used to represent the values that you can apply to the property. 默认情况下， 控件的属性 设置为 `AutoCompleteType.None` 。By default, the property for a control is set to `AutoCompleteType.None`. 在此设置下， 控件与 不同页上具有相同的其他控件共享列表 。With this setting, the control shares the list with other controls with the same across different pages. 还可以 基于类别（而不是基于）在控件间共享列表 。You can also share a list among controls based on a category instead of based on an . 将 属性设置为某个类别值 (例如 `AutoCompleteType.FirstName` 或) 时 `AutoCompleteType.LastName` ， 具有相同类别的所有控件共享同一列表。When you set the property to one of the category values (such as `AutoCompleteType.FirstName` or `AutoCompleteType.LastName`), all controls with the same category share the same list. 可以 通过将属性设置为来禁用控件的自动完成功能 `AutoCompleteType.Disabled` 。You can disable the AutoComplete feature for a control by setting the property to `AutoCompleteType.Disabled`. 有关配置和启用自动完成功能的详细信息，请参阅浏览器文档。Refer to your browser documentation for details on configuring and enabling the AutoComplete feature. 例如，若要在 Internet Explorer 版本5或更高版本中启用自动完成功能，请从 " **工具** " 菜单中选择 " **Internet 选项**"。For example, to enable the AutoComplete feature in Internet Explorer version 5 or later, from the **Tools** menu, choose **Internet Options**. 然后选择 " **内容** " 选项卡。选择 " **自动完成** " 按钮可以查看和修改自动完成功能的选项。Then choose the **Content** tab. Choose the **AutoComplete** button to view and modify options for the AutoComplete feature. ## Examples 下面的示例演示如何使用 枚举指定控件的自动完成类别 。The following example demonstrates how to use the enumeration to specify the AutoComplete category for a control. > [!IMPORTANT] > 此示例具有一个接受用户输入的文本框，这是一个潜在的安全威胁。This example has a text box that accepts user input, which is a potential security threat. 默认情况下，ASP.NET 网页验证用户输入是否不包含脚本或 HTML 元素。By default, ASP.NET Web pages validate that user input does not include script or HTML elements. 有关详细信息，请参阅[脚本侵入概述](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/aspnet/w1sw53ds(v=vs.100))。For more information, see [Script Exploits Overview](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/aspnet/w1sw53ds(v=vs.100)).
